421171457"}},{"from":{"fname":"zettel","id":"zettel","vaultName":"vault"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":160,"column":3,"offset":14949},"end":{"line":160,"column":28,"offset":14974},"indent":[]},"value":"zettel.20260421171636"},{"from":{"fname":"zettel.20260421171457","id":"zettel.20260421171457","vaultName":"vault"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":94,"column":3,"offset":7562},"end":{"line":94,"column":28,"offset":7587},"indent":[]},"value":"zettel.20260421171636"},{"from":{"fname":"zettel.20260421171825","id":"zettel.20260421171825","vaultName":"vault"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":64,"column":3,"offset":3256},"end":{"line":64,"column":28,"offset":3281},"indent":[]},"value":"zettel.20260421171636"},{"from":{"fname":"zettel.moc.ai-native","id":"zettel.moc.ai-native","vaultName":"vault"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":40,"column":3,"offset":3186},"end":{"line":40,"column":28,"offset":3211},"indent":[]},"value":"zettel.20260421171636"},{"from":{"fname":"zettel.moc.software-architecture","id":"zettel.moc.software-architecture","vaultName":"vault"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":54,"column":3,"offset":4025},"end":{"line":54,"column":28,"offset":4050},"indent":[]},"value":"zettel.20260421171636"}],"anchors":{"pertanyaan-yang-dibuka":{"type":"header","text":"Pertanyaan yang dibuka","value":"pertanyaan-yang-dibuka","line":15,"column":0,"depth":2},"klaim-utama":{"type":"header","text":"Klaim utama","value":"klaim-utama","line":21,"column":0,"depth":2},"fokus-bmad-technical-research":{"type":"header","text":"Fokus BMAD technical research","value":"fokus-bmad-technical-research","line":27,"column":0,"depth":2},"kenapa-ini-penting":{"type":"header","text":"Kenapa ini penting?","value":"kenapa-ini-penting","line":38,"column":0,"depth":2},"output-yang-berguna":{"type":"header","text":"Output yang berguna","value":"output-yang-berguna","line":44,"column":0,"depth":2},"lihat-juga":{"type":"header","text":"Lihat juga","value":"lihat-juga","line":55,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":[],"parent":"zettel","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"bmad-technical-research-memvalidasi-feasibility-sebelum-architecture\">BMAD technical research memvalidasi feasibility sebelum architecture<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#bmad-technical-research-memvalidasi-feasibility-sebelum-architecture\"></a></h1>\n<h2 id=\"pertanyaan-yang-dibuka\">Pertanyaan yang dibuka<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#pertanyaan-yang-dibuka\"></a></h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Apa yang ditanyakan BMAD technical research?</li>\n<li>Bagaimana ini berbeda dari riset pasar atau domain?</li>\n<li>Mengapa tahap ini penting sebelum solutioning?</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"klaim-utama\">Klaim utama<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#klaim-utama\"></a></h2>\n<p>BMAD technical research bukan mencari teknologi terbaru. Ia mencari kelayakan: apakah ide itu bisa dibangun, dengan biaya dan risiko yang masuk akal.</p>\n<p>BMAD menempatkan technical research pada analysis phase agar arsitektur tidak dimulai dari tebakan teknis.</p>\n<h2 id=\"fokus-bmad-technical-research\">Fokus BMAD technical research<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#fokus-bmad-technical-research\"></a></h2>\n<p>Di sini AI membantu menilai:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>apakah solusi potensial feasible,</li>\n<li>trade-off teknis utama apa,</li>\n<li>apakah ada pola arsitektur yang cocok,</li>\n<li>apa batas operasional dan biaya implementasinya.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Jika market research memvalidasi ide secara eksternal dan domain research memvalidasi logika internal, technical research memvalidasi sisi konstruksi.</p>\n<h2 id=\"kenapa-ini-penting\">Kenapa ini penting?<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#kenapa-ini-penting\"></a></h2>\n<p>Tanpa technical research, planning bisa jadi terlalu optimis. Anda bisa punya ide hebat dan pasar yang jelas, tetapi bila realisasi teknisnya mahal atau kompleks, produk itu bisa gagal di level operasional.</p>\n<p>Technical research menguji dasar feasibility sebelum arsitektur mulai mengambil keputusan.</p>\n<h2 id=\"output-yang-berguna\">Output yang berguna<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#output-yang-berguna\"></a></h2>\n<p>Setelah tahap ini, Anda harus punya gambaran tentang:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>opsi teknis utama yang realistis,</li>\n<li>risiko implementasi terbesar,</li>\n<li>asumsi teknis yang perlu diuji lagi,</li>\n<li>batasan desain awal.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Dengan begitu architecture dapat dibangun dari realitas teknis, bukan spekulasi.</p>\n<h2 id=\"lihat-juga\">Lihat juga<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#lihat-juga\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260421171635\">BMAD domain research memaksa pemahaman logika industri sebelum solusi</a> — BMAD domain research memaksa pemahaman logika industri sebelum solusi</li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260421171457\">BMAD analysis phase menghentikan ketidakjelasan sebelum berubah jadi PRD dan architecture</a> — BMAD analysis phase menghentikan ketidakjelasan sebelum berubah jadi PRD dan architecture</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"tags\">Tags<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#tags\"></a></h2>\n<ol>\n<li><a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">bmad (Private)</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">analysis-phase (Private)</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">technical-research (Private)</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">ai-native (Private)</a></li>\n</ol>\n<hr>\n<strong>Backlinks</strong>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel\">Zettelkasten</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260421171457\">BMAD analysis phase menghentikan ketidakjelasan sebelum berubah jadi PRD dan architecture</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260421171825\">Simulasi BMAD analysis phase: invoice app untuk freelancer</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.moc.ai-native\">MOC AI-native engineering</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.moc.software-architecture\">MOC: Software Architecture</a></li>\n</ul>","noteIndex":{"id":"root","title":"Hello and Welcome! 👋","desc":"","updated":1742030256619,"created":1646842475821,"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"fname":"root","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"vault"},"contentHash":"453f88f4a5f1ad7629ebb7cc49502125","links":[],"anchors":{"find-more":{"type":"header","text":"Find More","value":"find-more","line":20,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":["book-summaries","daily","handbook","notes","tags","til","zettel"],"parent":null,"data":{},"body":"\nWelcome to the homepage! I use Dendron to store and organize notes, ideas, and experiments I’m working on. Here are the main sections you’ll find on this site:\n\n1. **Learning Notes** — Practical notes on programming, recent technologies, and productivity tips.\n2. **Personal Projects** — Summaries of projects, experiments, and outcomes I’m working on or have completed.\n3. **Writings & Opinions** — Casual articles and reflections about technology, daily life, and other interesting topics.\n\nI’m constantly experimenting and learning. I hope the content here helps you as a reference, a starting point for discussion, or just light reading.\n\n> Why Dendron?\n>\nDendron helps keep notes organized. Its \"seed\" and \"vault\" concepts make it easy to structure content and find what you need.\n\n## Find More\n\nIf you want to learn more or connect, check these links:\n\n- [Homepage (Dendron)](https://zeihanaulia.g